         Somebody Save Me<br>
<br>
 Somebody save me. Somebody take my hand, don't let me fall, don't let me hit the wall. Pick me up, don't let me down; don't let my heart hit the ground. Can somebody hear me scream in pain? For this is no game. Where are you when I need you? I can't live without you. I crawl on my knees. Please, somebody save me from this disease! Somebody save me, somebody pick me up from these streets that bring me down. Catch my heart before it hits the ground. I reach out but no one is there, for no one seems to care. I lei here dying; my heart is crying, for no one is here to save me. Take me in your arms and hold me tight; tell me everything will be alright. Make me well; take this pain away that seems like hell. Save me from the things I see, for I wish they were'nt reality. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#5F9EA0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usasi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sasi</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://a1060.g.akamai.net/f/1060/597/30minutes/www.zing.com/picture/pad9e25fb1e1af65a8eddd5c924e825d5/feadd13d.gif height=25 width=20 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Genial Dictator</span><br> <font color=#000000>(5/18/01 5:44:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethestage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=200.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.thecaboose.net/sasi/Shugar.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A poem ~ Somebody Save Me</span><hr size=1> That's such a disturbing poem, hon!  It makes me want to reach out and hug the author tightly.<br>
